During our very long trip from Italy to France then Spain.  I admit this was one of my favorite meals. There is no menu but a man comes over to discuss your likes and dislikes. My daughter has worked for Coqueta so was very familiar with some of their dishes.  We had spinach salad ,  egg carpacio, octopus  (sauce was amazing), filet with foie gras. Everything was fresh and service was attentive. Thank you.
